\s18\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid10767046 \fs24\lang2057\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp1033 {\insrsid10767046\charrsid13844308 
It is useful to confine ourselves to this definition of trust:
\par "The subjective belief, perception, or conviction that information provided is true, factual, and objective, and that commitments undertaken, explicitly, or implicitly, will be honoured fully and in a timely manner".
\par Such perception, belief, or conviction are based on:
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid10767046\charrsid13844308 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}}\pard\plain \ql \fi-360\li720\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar
